A faithful adaptation of Richard Dennis's legendary Turtle Trading System, retuned for the weekly timeframe on NSE/BSE equities. Where the original Turtles traded daily commodity futures, this version trades weekly breakouts on Indian stocks — filtering out the noise of intraday swings and focusing on high-conviction trend moves that last weeks to months.
